    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>NMedia WordPress Member Conversation Plugin allow members to send and receive messages on any WordPress site.<br \/>\nLightning fast fronend UI. Setup in 5 seconds.<\/p>\n<h3>Setup<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Create a page<\/li>\n<li>paste this shortocde: [nmconvo]<\/li>\n<li>Admin Settings: Dashboard -&gt; WP Convo<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Features<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ajax based conversation<\/li>\n<li>Users List Modal<\/li>\n<li>New conversation notification<\/li>\n<li>All conversations list in admin<\/li>\n<li>Multi Language supported<\/li>\n<li>Sanitization applied<\/li>\n<li>Responsive Design<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/najeebmedia.com\/wordpress-plugin\/wordpress-front-end-member-private-message-with-file-attachment\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Demo &amp; Detail<\/a><\/p>\n<h3>Pro Features<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Control communication by roles<\/li>\n<li>File Attachment<\/li>\n<li>File Type, Size Control<\/li>\n<li>User list sorting, searching, pagination by DataTabe API<\/li>\n<li>Lifetime updates<\/li>\n<li>Pro Support Access<\/li>\n<li>Email Notification Extended Control<\/li>\n<li>Email Message Customization<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload plugin directory to the <code>\/wp-content\/plugins\/<\/code> directory<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress<\/li>\n<li>After activation, you can set options from <code>WP Convo<\/code> menu<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='how%20to%20use%20this%20plugin%20for%20my%20page%2Fpost'>\nHow to use this plugin for my page\/post\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Just place this shortcode [nmconvo]<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='can%20i%20see%20demo%3F'>\nCan I see Demo?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/filemanager.nmediahosting.com\/wp-convo\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Yes Sure, Click here<\/a><\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='how%20can%20admin%20see%20conversations'>\nHow can admin see conversations\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='any%20recommendation%20about%20design%3F'>\nAny Recommendation about design?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>You should have at least 500px wide space on page\/post to render this.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>2.1 May 25, 2019<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweaks: Remove variable form user role base function.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0 July 9, 2018<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Deprecated functions removed<\/li>\n<li>All new scripting<\/li>\n<li>Bootsrap with DataTables<\/li>\n<li>Fast UI<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.7<\/h4>\n<p>There was issue if Admin reply and then delete it, other user reply again to this then Admin only get notification all the time but can&#8217;t see it. So it is fixed<\/p>\n<h4>1.6<\/h4>\n<p>now you can place new message alert anywhere in site using shortcode <code>[nm-convo-alertbox pageurl=\"http:\/\/domain.com\/convopage_url\"]<\/code><\/p>\n<h4>1.5<\/h4>\n<p>multi language support is updated<\/p>\n<h4>1.4<\/h4>\n<p>douplaod.php and uploadify files have been removed and use wp core security<\/p>\n<h4>1.3<\/h4>\n<p>javascript bug is removed<\/p>\n<h4>1.2<\/h4>\n<p>Email notifcation feature is activated<br \/>\nunread message bug is removed<\/p>\n<h4>1.0<\/h4>\n<p>It is just born, will grow with time<\/p>\n",
